 <H1>Miss Stride Buffer</H1> 
 <P><UL>
<LI><H2>Mainly used to eliminate conflict miss
</H2>
</UL><UL>
<LI><H2>Prediction: if a memory address miss again after N other misses, the memory address is likely to miss again after N other misses
</H2>
</UL><UL>
<LI><H2>Scenario for the prediction to be useful
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>multiple loop nests
<LI>some variables or array elements are reused across iterations
</UL></UL></P>
